data.description: WASHER/DRYER AND FRIDGE INCLUDED! Located in a prime cul-de-sac, this 3 Bed/2 Bath/2 Car 1821 SF home comes with an extensive list of luxury features. Upon entering, find 18'' Palatina Corinth Tile Floors, New Wood Tile in the Primary Bedroom/Closet & Level 3 Carpet/Pad in 2 Secondary Beds. The Kitchen has Large Breakfast Bar w/pendant lighting overlooking Family & Dining Room & includes: 42'' Luxury Seacrest Birch Cabinets, Level 3 Granite, an Exotic Glass Backsplash w/Hidden Outlets, Under Cabinet Lighting & Built in Surround Sound System w/4 speakers in LR/DR. Primary Bed includes a spacious 10x10 Closet & Remodeled Super-Shower. Relax on the impressive 23'x16' TREX Deck, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Additional features include full floored attic, 5 outdoor outlets, 3 spigots, & 2 gates w/full sprinkler system (app controlled) as well as upgraded TRANE AC. Zoned to Top Rated Schools in KatyISD - Tompkins/Tays JR High/Woodcreek Elem. Don't miss this opportunity!
